00:22:35,516 --> 00:22:35,858
Scott: god.".

440
00:22:36,342 --> 00:22:37,958
Scott: Those other guys, yeah, they're pretty nerdy too.

441
00:22:38,640 --> 00:22:41,960
Scott: And they sing Yub Nub, the Ewok celebration song.

442
00:22:42,421 --> 00:22:46,400
Scott: And they have some subtitles so you can see what they mean, what the Ewok words mean.

443
00:22:46,903 --> 00:22:48,015
