Scott: And I can speak Boba Fett real well too.

459
00:23:35,508 --> 00:23:35,720
Rym: Yeah.

460
00:23:37,265 --> 00:23:37,940
Rym: Or even Jawa.

461
00:23:38,260 --> 00:23:39,074
Scott: I'm fluent, Boba Fett.

462
00:23:40,302 --> 00:23:40,935
Scott: Oh dee dee.

463
00:23:41,563 --> 00:23:42,014
Scott: Oh dee dee.

